{"article_id":"cSqlNSZfEdZXY4ma","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"California 's attorney general urges quick action","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to allow same-sex marriages","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"President Obama orders a review of federal statutes","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"after the law is stricken","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"The `` decisions put two giant cracks in the dark wall of discrimination , ''","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"advocate says","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"A deeply divided Supreme Court nudged the nation toward broad recognition of same-sex marriage on Wednesday in rulings","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"that advocates hailed as a `` joyous occasion ''","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"-- but still left many questions unanswered .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"Voting 5-4 in each of two decisions ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"justices threw out part of a law","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that denied hundreds of federal benefits to same-sex couples","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and cleared the way","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"for gays and lesbians to once again marry in California .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"At the same time , the high court declined to make a sweeping statement on the broader issue of same-sex marriage rights nationwide ,","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"rejecting California 's same-sex marriage ban","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"but leaving intact laws","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"banning such marriages in 35 other states .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"New Jersey has civil unions for same-sex couples ,","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"while New Mexico 's marriage law is gender neutral","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"and recognizes valid marriages","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"performed in other states .","depth":11},{"id":23,"text":"While the rulings fell short of the goal","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"same-sex marriage advocates have set","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"-- eliminating all laws","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"limiting the rights of gays and lesbians","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"to marry --","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"celebrations erupted outside the Supreme Court , as well as in San Francisco and around the country .","depth":5},{"id":29,"text":"In Washington , the couples","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"who sued","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"to dismantle the Defense of Marriage Act and its ban on federal benefits for same-sex couples","depth":8},{"id":32,"text":"emerged from the Supreme Court to thunderous cheers ,","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"simply holding their arms aloft in victory .","depth":7},{"id":34,"text":"In San Francisco , Crispin Hollins ,","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"who had already set a date for his wedding in the wake of the decision ,","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"there was too much to celebrate","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"to be disappointed by what the rulings did n't do .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"`` I 'm confident","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"that opinion in the United States is shifting towards being in favor of same-sex marriage ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"so it will simply take more time","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and allow the nation to come along in a way","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"that will provide more lasting support for equality , ''","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Toobin :","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"DOMA is gone","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"MUST WATCH Toobin :","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"DOMA is gone","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"01:04","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"Prop 8 attorney :","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"Wonderful day for U.S.","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"MUST WATCH Prop 8 attorney :","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"Wonderful day for U.S.","depth":10},{"id":58,"text":"02:45","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"Prop 8 plaintiff :","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"Our family is equal","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"MUST WATCH Prop 8 plaintiff :","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"Our family is equal","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"01:06","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"JUST WATCHED Prop 8 proposal :","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"He said yes !","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"MUST WATCH Prop 8 proposal :","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"He said yes !","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"01:12","depth":10},{"id":72,"text":"Opponents of same-sex marriage saw both peril and promise in the rulings ,","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"expressing dismay in the court 's decision on the Defense of Marriage Act","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"but taking some comfort in the decision","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"not to dismantle same-sex marriage bans nationwide .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` Their refusal","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"to redefine marriage for all states","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"is a major setback for those","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"seeking to redefine natural marriage , ''","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"said Family Research Council President Tony Perkins .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"`` Time is not on the side of those","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"seeking to create same-sex 'marriage . ' ''","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"In its divided ruling on the federal Defense of Marriage Act , the high court said","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"legally married same-sex couples must receive the same benefits","depth":13},{"id":85,"text":"provided to heterosexual couples .","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"The act had defined marriage as only between a man and a woman ,","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"but the court said","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"the law violated the rights of same-sex couples","depth":15},{"id":89,"text":"by demoting their marriages to second-class status","depth":16},{"id":90,"text":"when compared to their heterosexual peers .","depth":16},{"id":91,"text":"The court said","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"law wrongly `` instructs all federal officials , and indeed all persons","depth":15},{"id":93,"text":"with whom same-sex couples interact ,","depth":16},{"id":94,"text":"including their own children ,","depth":16},{"id":95,"text":"that their marriage is less worthy than the marriages of others . ''","depth":14},{"id":96,"text":"Now , the federal government recognizes the marriage of those same-sex couples","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"who are legally married in their states .","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"A divided high court also handed a victory to same-sex proponents","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"when it cleared the way","depth":12},{"id":100,"text":"for gay and lesbian couples to marry in California ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"dismissing an appeal to the state 's voter-approved Proposition 8","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"that banned such marriages .","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"The 5-4 decision avoids , for now , a sweeping conclusion","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"on whether same-sex marriage is a constitutional `` equal protection '' right","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that would apply to all states .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"In addition to restoring same-sex marriage in California ,","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"the decisions will eventually allow same-sex couples in states","depth":11},{"id":108,"text":"where they 're legally allowed to marry","depth":11},{"id":109,"text":"to apply for retirement , survivor and other benefits as married couples .","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"They 'll also be able to benefit from hundreds of other federal programs","depth":10},{"id":111,"text":"that have been , until now , reserved for heterosexual married couples under the Defense of Marriage Act 's definition of marriage as between a man and a woman .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"After the decisions were announced ,","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"President Barack Obama ordered a review of federal statutes","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"to ensure","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"the ruling is `` implemented swiftly and smoothly . ''","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"But he did n't give a more precise timeline .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"Defense Secretary Chuck Hagel said","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"he would work to get benefits to service members as soon as possible .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"`` That is now the law ,","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"and it is the right thing","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"to do , ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"It 's also unclear when same-sex marriages might resume in California .","depth":7},{"id":124,"text":"Gov . Jerry Brown said","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"he wants marriage licenses to begin flowing to gay and lesbian couples","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"the moment the 9th Circuit U.S. Court of Appeals confirms","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"that a court order","depth":14},{"id":128,"text":"preventing their issuance","depth":14},{"id":129,"text":"has been lifted .","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"Attorney General Kamala Harris said","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"weddings could begin","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"as soon as the order is lifted ,","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"which","depth":13},{"id":134,"text":"she said","depth":13},{"id":135,"text":"she was urging the court to do quickly .","depth":12},{"id":136,"text":"In Los Angeles , the county registrar 's office said","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"they 're ready .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"`` I did not count on them moving this far , ''","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"said New York Attorney General Eric Schneiderman ,","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"who called it the rulings `` an incredible victory . '' `` Today 's historic decisions put two giant cracks in the dark wall of discrimination","depth":14},{"id":141,"text":"that separates committed gay and lesbian couples from full equality , ''","depth":14},{"id":142,"text":"said Chad Griffin , president of the Human Rights Campaign ,","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"who called the rulings `` a joyous milestone . ''","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"`` While we celebrate the victory for Californians today ,","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"tomorrow we turn our attention to the millions of LGBT people","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"who do n't feel the reach of these decisions , ''","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"American University student Mollie Wagoner was waiting outside the Supreme Court for the decision with her girlfriend , Sharon Burk ,","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"when the word came down .","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"`` I do n't even have words .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"I 'm just so happy , and just overwhelmed with emotion , ''","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"she said .","depth":11},{"id":153,"text":"`` I could n't be more proud of my country and of the Supreme Court today .","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"I 'm so happy to be here","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"and be a part of it . ''","depth":11},{"id":156,"text":"Of course , not everyone was pleased by the ruling .","depth":8},{"id":157,"text":"While public opinion has shifted strongly toward support of same-sex marriage in recent years ,","depth":10},{"id":158,"text":"many conservatives , particularly faith-based conservatives , find the idea of same-sex marriage incomprehensible and dangerous .","depth":10},{"id":159,"text":"The Rev . Albert Mohler , president of the Southern Baptist Theological Seminary , found the decision on the Defense of Marriage Act ,","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"written by Justice Anthony Kennedy ,","depth":13},{"id":161,"text":"immensely troubling .","depth":12},{"id":162,"text":"`` Justice Kennedy 's opinion takes us to the brink of nationwide same-sex marriage .","depth":13},{"id":163,"text":"And I believe","depth":14},{"id":164,"text":"that will be a devastating thing for this country , ''","depth":14},{"id":165,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":166,"text":"Yes it will ,","depth":12},{"id":167,"text":"said John Eastman of the National Organization for Marriage .","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"`` When you destroy or redefine the institution ,","depth":13},{"id":169,"text":"all of society will be harmed , society","depth":14},{"id":170,"text":"that 's put such stock in the institution as a counterbalance to government and the way","depth":15},{"id":171,"text":"we raise and educate our children , ''","depth":15},{"id":172,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"Others on both sides found mixed messages in the rulings .","depth":4},{"id":174,"text":"Casey Miller said","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"he initially cheered Wednesday 's Supreme Court ruling","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"that essentially recognizes same-sex marriages .","depth":10},{"id":177,"text":"But ,","depth":10},{"id":178,"text":"he told CNN 's iReport ,","depth":11},{"id":179,"text":"`` As soon as I read some of the news articles","depth":13},{"id":180,"text":"describing the decision ,","depth":13},{"id":181,"text":"it sucked for us and for the majority of same-sex couples","depth":13},{"id":182,"text":"living in states with state marriage bans . ''","depth":13},{"id":183,"text":"Miller , 50 , married John Martin in California","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"before Proposition 8 was overturned .","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"The couple now lives in Texas","depth":7},{"id":186,"text":"where same-sex marriage is n't recognized .","depth":7},{"id":187,"text":"On the other side , the Rev . Rob Schenck , chairman of the Evangelical Church Alliance , said","depth":6},{"id":188,"text":"he was disappointed `` in the short-term results and the short-term questions","depth":8},{"id":189,"text":"that remain unsettled . '' `` But , ''","depth":9},{"id":190,"text":"he said ,","depth":9},{"id":191,"text":"`` the public conversation continues","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"and that 's a good thing . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":385,"left":0,"right":384,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":384,"left":236,"right":383,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":236,"left":214,"right":235,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":198,"right":213,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":198,"left":196,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":194,"right":195,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":194,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":200,"right":212,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":199,"right":9,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":199,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":212,"left":204,"right":211,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":204,"left":10,"right":203,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":203,"left":201,"right":202,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":15,"right":210,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":206,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":206,"left":16,"right":205,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":205,"left":17,"right":18,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":19,"right":208,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":20,"right":207,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":207,"left":21,"right":22,"relation":